WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
Here is ReplyPilot. Let’s follow one real support question from the moment it arrives.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.000
The customer shares their contact details, order number, and what went wrong.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:21.000
ReplyPilot identifies the category, urgency, and sentiment, then searches the company knowledge base.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:28.000
It prepares a professional response and shows its sources—but nothing is sent automatically.

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:37.000
A human reviews every word, makes changes, and approves the response.

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:44.000
Only human approval unlocks the send action.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:51.000
The approved email is delivered, and every step stays visible in the support dashboard.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:57.700
I’m John Venancio, an AI Automation Developer. Try the live demo, or contact me.
